Cit14_3-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Peter Simpson (26 August 2014). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ottawacitizen.com/news/local-news/oscar-peterson-statue-defaced-vandalism-or-social-comment\">\"Oscar Peterson statue vandals caught on video; sculptor reacts\"</a>. <i>Ottawa Citizen</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">15 August</span> 2015</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Ottawa+Citizen&amp;rft.atitle=Oscar+Peterson+statue+vandals+caught+on+video%3B+sculptor+reacts&amp;rft.date=2014-08-26&amp;rft.au=Peter+Simpson&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fottawacitizen.com%2Fnews%2Flocal-news%2Foscar-peterson-statue-defaced-vandalism-or-social-comment&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AStatue+of+Oscar+Peterson\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-OtCit15-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-OtCit15_4-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Peter Hum (15 August 2015). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ottawacitizen.com/entertainment/local-arts/the-timeless-appeal-of-oscar-peterson\">\"The timeless appeal of Oscar Peterson\"</a>. <i>Ottawa Citizen</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">15 August</span> 2015</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Ottawa+Citizen&amp;rft.atitle=The+timeless+appeal+of+Oscar+Peterson&amp;rft.date=2015-08-15&amp;rft.au=Peter+Hum&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fottawacitizen.com%2Fentertainment%2Flocal-arts%2Fthe-timeless-appeal-of-oscar-peterson&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AStatue+of+Oscar+Peterson\" class=\"Z3988\">